WEBVTT

00:00:01.311 --> 00:00:04.325
TAPE NUMBER THREE, MR ISAAC DANIELS.

00:00:04.433 --> 00:00:07.987
dertseylt mir nokh vos iz vos hot pasirt dernokh?

00:00:08.483 --> 00:00:09.979
vos hot pasirt.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:09.996
yo.

00:00:13.933 --> 00:00:18.551
azoy vi ikh hob gearbet un ikh hob shoyn gehat dray mentshn.

00:00:20.363 --> 00:00:27.984
iz tsu mir arayngekumen tsvey mener, tsvey partners, zenen geven partners, vos zey makhn mebl.

00:00:30.538 --> 00:00:35.226
zey geyen arum in oyf di shenste gesheftn vu s'do mebl

00:00:35.226 --> 00:00:40.219
un zey nemen arop a PICTURE un zey makhn mebl.

00:00:40.275 --> 00:00:43.137
prekhtik mebl. endlekh tsu dos.

00:00:43.752 --> 00:00:47.610
un er bashtelt zey viln do mir makhn a gantse SET.

00:00:47.667 --> 00:00:54.663
betn, a shrank, demolts iz geven modish a shrank a groysn mit fir tirn.

00:00:55.598 --> 00:01:03.961
un aza min tualetke mit a shpigl, un un ANYWAY un vos nokh, a a a tishele a sheyns,

00:01:05.233 --> 00:01:08.332
un er bashtelt zikh bay mir ikh zol ikh zol zey makhn

00:01:08.338 --> 00:01:11.741
tsvey SUITS mit kots, m'kumt adurkh mitn prayz.

00:01:12.068 --> 00:01:14.610
zog ikh, ven vestu dos hobn fertik?

00:01:14.683 --> 00:01:18.086
zogt er, ven du vest hobn fertik di SUITS vet dir dos zayn fertik.

00:01:18.126 --> 00:01:19.689
mayn froy veyst nisht derfun.

00:01:21.484 --> 00:01:23.874
ANYWAY, kurts makhn di geshikhte,

00:01:26.057 --> 00:01:30.691
der ROOM, ikh hob gehat eyn tsimer, der tsimer iz geven zeyer a groyse.

00:01:31.187 --> 00:01:34.353
hob ikh arayngenumen a CARPENTER, oykhet a fraynt,

00:01:34.647 --> 00:01:41.070
un s'geven di v- di di di vant di geven fir vin- vindes, azoy groys iz geven di tsimer.

00:01:41.464 --> 00:01:46.992
hot er ibergetsoygn, do hot men gearbet un do iz gevezn mayn mayn mayn betl.

00:01:48.568 --> 00:01:51.852
un m'hot gemakht di di FLOORS mit mayses gesheftn,

00:01:52.197 --> 00:01:56.325
kurts makhn di geshikhte, m'hot di FURNITURE arayngeshtelt. alts gevorn fertik.

00:01:57.259 --> 00:02:00.327
un un mayn froy iz gevezn oyf zumer voynung,

00:02:00.327 --> 00:02:05.989
s'gevezn shoyn noent tsu di yomim-toyvim, un zi iz aheymgekumen.

00:02:05.989 --> 00:02:12.103
zi get a kum arayn, geefnt oyf di tir, zi blaybt shteyn, zi veyst nisht tsi do do voynt.

00:02:12.649 --> 00:02:17.098
vos iz geshen? zi heybt nisht on tsu visn. s'iz ir freyd gemeynt.

00:02:19.686 --> 00:02:25.215
THAT'S IT, do hob ikh gevoynt, un s'hot zikh fargresert di J- di JOB.

00:02:25.390 --> 00:02:28.523
ikh hob ongehoybn tsu krign PRIVATE CLIENTAL.

00:02:28.883 --> 00:02:36.605
fun vanen zey hobn zikh dervust, zenen gekumen, ikh hob gehat akht mentshn, tsu der arbet.

00:02:38.569 --> 00:02:42.005
un mayne ale khaveyrim hobn gezogt, nu, er iz shoyn an oyfgearbeter.

00:02:44.931 --> 00:02:53.498
FINALLY, nokh tsvey yor, dos iz gevezn in fir un draysikstn,

00:02:53.757 --> 00:03:01.294
ende in zeks un draysikstn yor, in ts- in nayntstn APRIL iz geboyrn gevorn mayn tokhter.

00:03:02.245 --> 00:03:03.651
vos iz ir nomen?

00:03:03.578 --> 00:03:04.551
Dine.

00:03:06.649 --> 00:03:09.748
zi iz geboyrn gevorn in a shpitol, oder in der heym?

00:03:08.691 --> 00:03:11.284
in a shpitol. yo..

00:03:11.391 --> 00:03:19.839
un in dem shpitol lozt men nisht arayn VISITn, zen, absolut nisht. tsen teg, ABSOLUTELY nisht.

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:22.607
un nisht dem man, nisht keyn keynem nisht.

00:03:22.933 --> 00:03:25.002
nor ikh hob dokh fort gevolt zen.

00:03:26.410 --> 00:03:32.968
gey ikh tsu tsum shpitol, un der un ikh ze a NURSE,

00:03:33.919 --> 00:03:38.182
vos zi iz oyf di FLOOR vu mayn froy iz ligt.

00:03:39.825 --> 00:03:44.477
nem ikh aroys tsvey zlotes, "ikh vel zen mayn froy."

00:03:44.517 --> 00:03:48.796
zogt zi, "vart tsu, yetst geyen di doktoyrim arum, zey ebn avekgeyn."

00:03:49.090 --> 00:03:54.048
ven di doktoyrim zenen avekgegangen, iz iz gegangen zi hot mir gegebn a doktershe khalat,

00:03:54.048 --> 00:03:58.280
ikh hob ongeton mit a tshepik oyfn kop, un ikh kum arayn.

00:03:58.354 --> 00:04:03.151
mayn froy k- zi veyst nisht ver dos iz. zi derkent mir nisht.

00:04:03.151 --> 00:04:07.511
zogt zi, "vi arum bistu do arayngekumen, s'dokh ummeglekh do." s'geven a kristlekh

00:04:07.804 --> 00:04:11.730
shpitol far bloyz far kimpetorins.

00:04:08.850 --> 00:04:09.704
shpitol.

00:04:11.820 --> 00:04:16.269
ANYWAY, ikh bin aheymgekumen fayn, alts iz geven in bestn ordenung.

00:04:18.402 --> 00:04:20.938
un ven ikh hob shoyn gekoyft di voynung,

00:04:20.938 --> 00:04:25.246
hob ikh, iz mayn yingerer bruder, er hot gevoynt in Lukov.

00:04:25.455 --> 00:04:27.507
er hot geFINISHt di PUBLIC SCHOOL,

00:04:27.953 --> 00:04:31.946
un vos er hot nisht gehat vos tsu tun, hot men geshikt im tsu mir, iz er gekumen tsu mir.

00:04:32.053 --> 00:04:38.916
iz er geshtanen mit mir. un vi dos kind iz geboyrn gevorn iz ho- hob ikh genumen mayn muter tsu mir.

00:04:39.023 --> 00:04:45.075
ze'mir geven a familye tsuzamen. un azoy ho'mir gevoynt tsunazamen.

00:04:46.752 --> 00:04:55.756
ikh bin geven, vi zogt men es, nisht shlekht UP. biz nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:04:57.585 --> 00:05:01.629
vos hot demolts pasirt? vi azoy iz geven dem ershtn tog,

00:05:02.260 --> 00:05:06.068
ven der ershter tog fun der milkhome, vos hot,

00:05:04.900 --> 00:05:11.737
dos iz geven a fraytik, m'hot nisht der- Hitler hot nisht derklert keyn milkhome in Poyln.

00:05:12.705 --> 00:05:14.825
nor m'hot gehert m'bombardirt.

00:05:14.950 --> 00:05:18.538
iz men aroysgelofn kukn, iz shoyn geven a froy a gehargete,

00:05:18.561 --> 00:05:21.170
oyf der anderer zayt STREET vu ikh hob gevoynt.

00:05:22.223 --> 00:05:27.195
iz bald iz gevezn, m'hot shoyn gemoldn az Hitler iz ongefaln oyf Poyln,

00:05:28.332 --> 00:05:35.801
un m'hot ongehoybn shoyn gegangen dos militer iz gegangen alts tsu der grenets, tsu der daytshisher grenets.

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:41.623
un di bombardirung iz geven geferlekh. geferlekh.

00:05:44.869 --> 00:05:51.174
s'gevezn bay undz vu ikh hob gevoynt iz oyf dem ferde FLOOR iz geven a dru- a drukanye.

00:05:51.298 --> 00:05:54.802
ir veyst a druk-mashin. iz arayn a tsind-bombe.

00:05:55.264 --> 00:06:00.135
bin ikh aroyf oyfn dortn oyfn dakh, ikh un nokh a por BOYS,

00:06:00.546 --> 00:06:07.070
un m'hot di bombe blokn PAPERS vos zey hobn gebrent aropgevorfn aron in hoyf arayn.

00:06:07.330 --> 00:06:13.787
mayn muter iz geshtanen un hot geshrign, geveynt zi hot geveynt, gey arop! un do zenen gefloygn di eroplanen.

00:06:14.147 --> 00:06:19.102
ikh hob gehat a gefil az mir vet gornisht geshen. epes aza gefil hob ikh gehat.

00:06:20.408 --> 00:06:30.138
ikh hob getrogn, ikh bin gevorn tsugeteylt, fun fun hoyf dortn fun der fun der regirung, hob ikh getrogn do a vayse lente,

00:06:30.921 --> 00:06:34.829
az ikh hob gekent geyn bay nakht. vayl s'dokh geven gornisht keyn LIGHTS.

00:06:35.545 --> 00:06:39.824
az m'hot gedorfn geyn epes vos UNK hob ikh gekent geyn dos.

00:06:42.767 --> 00:06:49.612
biz yomkiper. vayl ikh far yomkiper, eb ikh dir zogn,

00:06:51.205 --> 00:06:58.101
iz der b- di kuzine fun Prage, hot arayngeMOVEt keyn Varshe tsu ir shvester.

00:06:58.410 --> 00:07:01.931
di shvester hot gevoynt nisht vayt fun mir.

00:07:02.494 --> 00:07:08.107
un der man irer iz gevezn a lyubavitsher khosid, der foter UNK iz geven a khosid.

00:07:08.890 --> 00:07:11.499
hot men yomkiper dortn gedavnt.

00:07:12.535 --> 00:07:15.375
nor ven zey hobn arayngeMIVEt do aher,

00:07:15.375 --> 00:07:23.615
iz bay zey in hoyz iz geblibn bobelekh un zek mel un fun tsuker un vos ir vilt ⟨hungerik⟩.

00:07:25.584 --> 00:07:30.517
z- zey viln nisht geyn, m'bombardirt, m'vil oyfraysn di brik

00:07:31.418 --> 00:07:36.322
vos s'grenetst Prage mit Varshe fareynikt, iber di Vaysl.

00:07:38.252 --> 00:07:40.726
vemenen bet men? mikh.

00:07:43.602 --> 00:07:47.359
trakht ikh mir, ikh vel geyn, efsher vel ikh nemen a bisele mel far mir oykhet.

00:07:49.609 --> 00:07:52.185
ober dos bombardirn iz geferlekh.

00:07:52.512 --> 00:07:58.884
gey ikh di gantse tsayt bay di bay di vent bay di BUILDINGS, shar ikh zikh nenter tsu der brik.

00:08:00.612 --> 00:08:04.841
un vos a UNK fun bombes falt nisht oyf der brik, s'falt in Vaysl arayn.

00:08:05.944 --> 00:08:11.726
un ikh hob zikh gegebn, di brik iz bay MORE OF A QUARTER MILE.

00:08:12.677 --> 00:08:17.694
un ikh hob zikh gegebn a loz oyf di brik loyfn, ariber.

00:08:17.694 --> 00:08:22.217
un dortn iz gevezn aza RAVINE, bin ikh bald a- aropgeshprungen in RAVINE arayn,

00:08:22.217 --> 00:08:23.792
ANYWAY, ikh bin ariber dortn.

00:08:24.270 --> 00:08:29.951
ikh bin arayn in hoyz arayn, un ikh hob genumen a bisl dos dos dos, UNK.

00:08:30.700 --> 00:08:34.983
un krik di zelbe zakh. un ikh bin,

00:08:33.265 --> 00:08:35.025
vi azoy hot ir dos geshlept?

00:08:35.936 --> 00:08:42.843
az men darf shlept men. mer vi m'ken. un s'gring. vayl du muzt.

00:08:45.162 --> 00:08:50.842
ikh hob es gebrengt. un dos iz geven erev yomkiper.

00:08:51.625 --> 00:08:57.508
yomkiper hot men gedavnt bay zey in hoyz, bay mayn kuzine. in in Varshe.

00:08:57.818 --> 00:09:02.655
ir flegt geyn in shul arayn v- in der tsayt ven ir hot gelebt in Varshe?

00:09:03.150 --> 00:09:07.042
oyf di yomim-toyvim fleg ikh a mol yo geyn. vu bin ikh gegangen?

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:13.168
ikh bin gegangen hern Kosevitski. dortn bin ikh gegangen. ikh hob lib gehat tsu hern a khazn.

00:09:14.457 --> 00:09:17.423
ikh hob zikh shoyn gekent mit dem JANITOR.

00:09:17.423 --> 00:09:21.571
host im gegebn tsvey zlotes hot er dikh arayngelozt nokh an anderer tir.

00:09:21.578 --> 00:09:24.457
az bist arayngekumen INSIDE hot men dir nisht kontrolirt.

00:09:25.864 --> 00:09:28.085
farkert, m'hot dir gegebn vu tsu zitsn oykh.

00:09:29.391 --> 00:09:36.539
SO dortn ho- hot men gedavnt, der der foter zayner, alts khasidim.

00:09:36.664 --> 00:09:43.183
eyn eyn zun iz gevezn, take mayn kuzin's foter's der der eltster zun,

00:09:43.183 --> 00:09:51.288
iz gevezn der khazn in Riga barn rebn, barn Lyubavitsher rebn. geven groyse khsidim.

00:09:52.020 --> 00:09:58.039
UNK yom-kiper iz arayn a bombe un s'hot ongehoybn tsu brenen der hoyf.

00:09:59.158 --> 00:10:00.924
ikh bin nokh nisht geven opgebrent.

00:10:01.825 --> 00:10:07.657
mayn voynung, fun fun mayn kuzine iz geven azoy vi azoy vi a keygn iber, nisht vayt.

00:10:08.119 --> 00:10:13.243
un do brent. trakht ikh mir azoy. yener, ikh bin do do un dortn, lomikh zen vos tut zikh dortn.

00:10:13.485 --> 00:10:19.470
ikh bin aroys oyf der gas, MIDNIGHT. shvarts. fun di bombes.

00:10:20.050 --> 00:10:27.232
s'brent arum un arum fayer, s'brent. Varshe brent. ikh bin in der mitn.

00:10:28.302 --> 00:10:31.924
un vu zenen vu iz geven di froy mit der mit der kind?

00:10:32.419 --> 00:10:37.610
di froy bi- iz dokh geven bay zikh in hoyz. mitn mitn bruder un di mame.

00:10:37.887 --> 00:10:42.639
nor ikh bin gevezn do o, vos ikh hob gebrengt di UNK, zog ikh ikh vel nemen a bisele.

00:10:43.607 --> 00:10:46.942
zog ikh, az s'brent do, vu, lomikh zen vos tut zikh dortn.

00:10:47.100 --> 00:10:50.030
ikh loyf aroys, vi ikh zog az s'brent arum un arum.

00:10:50.391 --> 00:10:55.346
ikh gib a kum tsu loyfn in hoyf arayn, mayn hoyz brent.

00:10:55.723 --> 00:11:01.387
di fentster ofn, un ikh ze s- s'fayer INSIDE, s'brent umetum.

00:11:01.427 --> 00:11:07.800
ikh hob nisht keyn vayb, nisht keyn kind, nisht keyn mame. bay mir keynem. ikh hob nisht keyn eynem.

00:11:10.354 --> 00:11:15.056
heyb ikh zikh on tsu fregn, s'gevorn a bisele shtiler,

00:11:15.231 --> 00:11:19.159
heyb ikh on tsu fregn di shkheynim vos zey hobn do gevoynt,

00:11:19.159 --> 00:11:22.886
a sakh kumen krik tsu tsum hoyf a kuk gebn.

00:11:23.078 --> 00:11:31.729
freg ikh zikh, "efsher hot ets gezen di froy?" "yo, m'hot ir gezen, zi iz arayngelofn in in hoyf arayn numer eyn un draysik."

00:11:33.355 --> 00:11:46.967
ikh loyf tsu tsu dem eyn un draysik, s'ayngefaln di hoyf.

00:11:48.930 --> 00:11:54.054
un mayn kind hot getrogn a por vayse shikhlekh, mit zi hot gehat vayse zoklekh,

00:11:55.056 --> 00:12:00.163
un fun unter di di di grozn shtekt aroys tsvey fiselekh

00:12:01.603 --> 00:12:04.921
mit shikhelekh, ikh ze az dos hot mayn tokhter getrogn.

00:12:08.337 --> 00:12:10.558
zog ikh, do arum zenen zey umgekumen.

00:12:14.226 --> 00:12:18.810
shtey un veyn, ikh ze nisht keynemen.

00:12:20.166 --> 00:12:22.100
nisht dem bruder, nisht di mame.

00:12:26.562 --> 00:12:32.363
dos iz shoyn gevezn ariber di nakht, tsu morgns,

00:12:32.363 --> 00:12:37.693
ruft arum mayns a ⟨zak⟩, ikh gib a kuk, mayn froy geyt mitn kind.

00:12:38.070 --> 00:12:41.472
un fun anderer zayt geyt mayn bruder un di mame.

00:12:42.154 --> 00:12:46.400
vu bistu gevezn? zi iz gelofn azoy fun danen,

00:12:47.132 --> 00:12:52.846
s'hot ongehoybn do tsu brenen, hot zi gekhapt dos kind un un s'hot zi gedokhtn az dortn brent nisht.

00:12:52.903 --> 00:12:58.905
iz zi geloyfn azoy vayt vu ikh zol aykh zogn, azoy in dan aroys tsu COLLEGE.

00:13:00.193 --> 00:13:02.887
oyf a gas hot zi geheysn Tvarde.

00:13:03.130 --> 00:13:10.194
dortn hob ikh gehat a khaver, un der khaver hot gevoynt in a h- in a hoyf

00:13:10.200 --> 00:13:15.104
vu er hot gehat a mishpokhe, hobn zey gehat a restoran in LOW in BASEMENT.

00:13:15.499 --> 00:13:20.659
iz zi gelofn un zi hot im getrofn barn toyer, hot er ir farhaltn, un vu loyfstu?

00:13:20.659 --> 00:13:24.692
er hot ir arayngenumen, m'hot ir aropgenumen un di restoran arayn,

00:13:24.692 --> 00:13:27.879
un m'hot dos kind avekgeleygt oyfn tish s'zol shlofn.

00:13:28.442 --> 00:13:30.866
un zi hot dortn ibergenekhtikt di nakht.

00:13:32.188 --> 00:13:36.851
un zi eyder, un un bay tog in der fri hot men vayter bombardirt, zi hot nisht gekent

00:13:36.851 --> 00:13:40.738
azoy s'gevorn a bisele shtiler, iz iz gekumen mitn kind mit ir.

00:13:40.845 --> 00:13:45.058
shte- shtelt dikh for shtel di freyd. m'hot geveynt un gefreyt zikh.

00:13:47.308 --> 00:13:50.727
ikh bin opgebrent gevorn, un dos alts farbrent gevorn, vos iz gevezn.

00:13:51.223 --> 00:13:53.461
farzikherung iz demolts nisht geven?

00:13:52.253 --> 00:13:56.668
ikh hob nor getrogn azoy tsvey SUITS oyf zikh, un a mantl.

00:13:56.927 --> 00:13:59.621
IN CASE vos ven zol ikh hob vos tsu farkoyfn.

00:14:01.028 --> 00:14:06.557
s'iz geven a farzikherung demolts oder, farzikherung? INSURANCE.

00:14:06.416 --> 00:14:11.332
vos redt ir?! vos far a INSURANCE? s'keyn mol in Poyln keyn INSURANCE nisht gevezn.

00:14:06.715 --> 00:14:08.100
gornisht.

00:14:11.406 --> 00:14:13.993
efsher di raykhe mentshn hobn zikh efsher INSURED,

00:14:13.993 --> 00:14:17.441
vi? ikh ikh her dos ershte mol Poyln iz geven INSURANCE.

00:14:18.409 --> 00:14:24.781
ikh hob gehat lign gelt in s'hot geheysn ⟨Pekorl⟩.

00:14:25.851 --> 00:14:29.793
dort hot men gekent DEPOSITn gelt, hob ikh gehat dortn lign.

00:14:29.833 --> 00:14:33.743
un azoy vi er hot zikh gemakht di gesheftn, UNK er hot geSTOPt, nisht aroysgegebn keyn gelt.

00:14:34.170 --> 00:14:35.564
ikh bin geblibn on gelt.

00:14:38.794 --> 00:14:47.394
ANYWAY, ikh hob gehat a bruder voynen, take der eltster bruder hot gevoynt oyf di Novelipe akht un tsvontsik.

00:14:47.839 --> 00:14:50.651
UNK efsher iz er nisht opgebrent gevorn.

00:14:50.657 --> 00:14:56.794
hot men ongehoybn zikh tsu sharn nokh heyf adurkhgehakte zen dortn ahin.

00:14:57.323 --> 00:15:00.253
shoyn geven a shverer veg tsutsugeyn tsun im.

00:15:00.495 --> 00:15:03.847
s- m'hot azoy bombardirt, s'geven oysergeveyntlekh.

00:15:04.596 --> 00:15:10.783
in yenem tog un yene nakht, ven mayn froy iz antlofn,

00:15:11.869 --> 00:15:16.081
zenen geharget gevorn finef un akhtsik toyznt mentshn.

00:15:20.222 --> 00:15:23.152
ikh bin ongekumen tsu mayn bruder, di voynung iz geshtanen.

00:15:23.614 --> 00:15:26.004
ze'mir ale arayngegangen dortn tsun im.

00:15:26.567 --> 00:15:29.987
oyfn hoyf iz geven a khsidish shtibl.

00:15:33.351 --> 00:15:38.373
yo, ANYWAY, m'iz dortn gevezn far a vayl.

00:15:38.937 --> 00:15:43.217
dervayle azoy Poyln hot zikh untergegebn,

00:15:44.573 --> 00:15:51.536
hot men shoyn nisht bombardirt, nor Hitler hot nisht gevolt arayngeyn mit der armey, biz vanen m'vet nisht opCLEANen di gasn.

00:15:53.112 --> 00:15:56.734
flegt men khapn mentshn tsivilne zoln reynikn di gasn.

00:15:58.613 --> 00:16:01.526
ikh hob gehat aza mazl, ikh bin aroysgegangen hot men mikh gekhapt.

00:16:02.157 --> 00:16:03.940
azoy az ikh hob nisht getort aroysgeyn.

00:16:06.527 --> 00:16:14.233
ANYWAY, s'hot shoyn ge- ongehoybn ontsukumen furn mit produktn fun yener zayt.

00:16:16.399 --> 00:16:26.906
fun fun di rusisher zayt. mit produktn. dervayl, un un far keyn gelt tsu koyfn hob ikh nisht gehat.

00:16:27.351 --> 00:16:30.452
hob ikh bashlosn mit mit der froy az zi zol a-

00:16:30.452 --> 00:16:35.107
ikh hob geshaft a fur vu zi tsu forn do vu ir mume voynt.

00:16:35.670 --> 00:16:41.081
s'a bisl a bisl far a shtikl vegs eyder m'iz gekumen tsu tsu der mume.

00:16:41.155 --> 00:16:45.334
zog ikh, di best zakh, for tsu der mumen, vestu hobn tsu esn mitn kind.

00:16:46.656 --> 00:16:52.657
ikh vel zen do vos s'do vos vet do zayn, der bruder un di mame,. ikh ken dokh nisht azoy antloyfn.

00:16:54.115 --> 00:16:55.746
ikh hob geshaft, zi iz avekgeforn.

00:16:58.215 --> 00:17:00.926
un dos kind iz krank gevorn oyfn veg,

00:17:02.788 --> 00:17:05.988
s'hot ir ongehoybn zi hot gekrign a disen- disenterye.

00:17:07.917 --> 00:17:10.915
ANYWAY koym vos zi hot zikh dershlept dortn ahin mitn kind.

00:17:10.887 --> 00:17:13.513
mit vos iz zi geforn?

00:17:12.357 --> 00:17:13.566
oyf a fur.

00:17:14.652 --> 00:17:18.729
koym zey hobn zikh dershlept zikh ahin, vayl m'hot der dokter mit ⟨mayses⟩.

00:17:18.734 --> 00:17:20.415
dos kind iz gezunt gevorn.

00:17:23.325 --> 00:17:34.609
un ikh un der yingerer bruder, azoy vi s'geven shtil, zenen ongekumen fun Dantsik

00:17:34.682 --> 00:17:40.821
barshtn, du veyst vos barshtn zenen? nisht keyn shif, s'iz azoy vi a shif, OH NO,

00:17:40.821 --> 00:17:45.645
nor di groyse groyse groyse BOATS, mit rayz.

00:17:47.001 --> 00:17:51.754
nu s'hot nisht gekent tsugeyn tsum breg, shteyt es a bisl avek fun breg.

00:17:53.076 --> 00:17:58.453
hot men geleygt breter, do a bret biz arayn INSIDE.

00:17:58.763 --> 00:18:01.187
keyn yidn hobn di goyim nisht arayngelozt.

00:18:02.627 --> 00:18:08.662
ikh mit mayn bruder ze'mir tsugekumen, m'hot gehat genumen barn tsvey tsikhlekh fun fun kishns,

00:18:09.158 --> 00:18:12.816
un ikh hob mir arop gerukt dem kapelitsh iber di oygn, un mayn bruder azoy,

00:18:12.816 --> 00:18:15.094
un m'hot zikh a kh- a glitsh arayn gegebn

00:18:15.094 --> 00:18:21.402
in der barsht arayn, m'hot ongenumen tsvey z- tsikhlekh mit rayz, un m'iz aroys.

00:18:21.780 --> 00:18:24.359
nu di simkhe bay undz beyde iz geven groys,

00:18:24.359 --> 00:18:27.225
m'vet araynkumen tsum bruder, s'vet zayn vos tsu kokhn.

00:18:28.513 --> 00:18:31.072
azoy vi mir geyen mit di tsvey zeklekh,

00:18:31.348 --> 00:18:36.826
iz fun a hoyf shpringt aroys tsvey zelner, zenen dort geshtanen mit shikses INSIDE,

00:18:37.390 --> 00:18:40.911
un m'hot undz gut ongeshlogn azoy vi es gehert tsu zayn, m'hot tsugenumen.

00:18:42.013 --> 00:18:45.854
dos zenen geven daytshe dzh- zelner?

00:18:42.030 --> 00:18:45.905
m'iz ahey- mit a NO, poylisher zelner.

00:18:46.418 --> 00:18:49.551
un m'aheymgekumen mit gornisht.

00:18:53.556 --> 00:19:00.131
s'geven a fraytik un di yidn zenen gekumen davenen dortn in shtibl arayn,

00:19:01.032 --> 00:19:03.304
un s'hot shoyn ongehoybn ontsukumen daytshn.

00:19:06.465 --> 00:19:11.454
ikh bin geven bay mayn bruder, un ikh kuk aroys nokhn fentster,

00:19:11.781 --> 00:19:15.150
loyfn daytshn arayn in dem shtibl arayn,

00:19:15.612 --> 00:19:22.054
un m'shlogt un m'harget, un di yidn loyfn aroys fun dortn, di hent in der heykh, reboyne-shel-oylem!

00:19:22.054 --> 00:19:26.877
un di daytshn yogn zey, m'hakt azoy bay di kep iber ale, az s'groylekh.

00:19:28.167 --> 00:19:30.388
zog ikh tsu mayn bruder,

00:19:31.693 --> 00:19:36.547
ikh ken dos nisht zen, ikh ken dos nisht tsukukn, ikh muz avek fun danen.

00:19:38.477 --> 00:19:43.584
di ⟨yingern⟩ bruder mayn muter vil im nisht lozn im kumen. im vil zi hobn mit zikh.

00:19:44.569 --> 00:19:47.907
der tsveyter bruder zi zogt az zey forn s'vet forn

00:19:47.907 --> 00:19:51.128
tsum tatn, tsu di eltern dortn bay der ban vu zey voynen.

00:19:54.357 --> 00:20:00.509
ikh mit nokh dray khaveyrim bashlisn mir dos iz frayt- s'shabes far tog,

00:20:02.372 --> 00:20:04.560
ikh bin nokh fraytik ikh bin nokh gegangen

00:20:04.566 --> 00:20:08.930
ikh hob farkoyft a SUIT tsu a kristlekhn shnayder, ikh zol hobn a por zlotes.

00:20:09.342 --> 00:20:14.415
un s'shabes far tog bin ikh aroys fun Varshe,

00:20:15.602 --> 00:20:25.957
un tsu fus, m'iz gegangen. iz men opgegangen tsvey un fuftsik kilometer, mayl, a vayt veg,

00:20:26.706 --> 00:20:29.450
m'iz ongekumen far nakht dortn ahin,

00:20:31.515 --> 00:20:36.454
iz men arayn tsu a yidisher familye, undz hobn moyre gehat vos an emes,

00:20:36.949 --> 00:20:43.136
zenen zey gegangen zey hobn oyfgehongen oyf der tir a spane mit a tifus. a PAPER OUTSIDE.

00:20:43.564 --> 00:20:47.878
di daytshn hobn dos derzen, UNK nisht arayngekumen, zey hobn moyre gehat.

00:20:48.475 --> 00:20:53.362
hobn ibergenekhtikt dortn di nakht, un far tog vayter.

00:20:53.537 --> 00:20:58.357
alts m'hot getsoygn tsu der grenets tsu tsu der rusisher g- grenets.

00:20:59.157 --> 00:21:01.378
tsu morgns iz men vayter gegangen,

00:21:02.110 --> 00:21:06.896
un m'iz gegangen keyn a shtetl hot es geheysn Sokolov.

00:21:07.847 --> 00:21:09.900
m'iz ongekumen dortn oykh far nakht.

00:21:11.104 --> 00:21:14.417
vos an emes bin ikh arayngekumen tsu mayn froy's,

00:21:14.417 --> 00:21:19.367
zenen gevezn a mishpokhe MULTI-milyonern.

00:21:21.735 --> 00:21:24.744
zey hobn gehat fabrikn fun tsuker un fun dem un

00:21:24.744 --> 00:21:29.461
un z- zey flegn makhn far di poyern di groyse peltsn azelkhe dos.

00:21:29.461 --> 00:21:31.368
a zeyer raykh, zey hobn gehat

00:21:31.368 --> 00:21:36.798
gazolin STATIONS vos do hobn zey. ZEY zoln gebn azoy groys, NO.

00:21:38.256 --> 00:21:41.625
nu ikh hob nokh gehat epes a por zlotes, bin ikh gegangen ikh hob aroys-

00:21:41.766 --> 00:21:46.806
tsu a beker m'hot gekoyft a broyt, m'hot gekoyft a vursht, m'hot opgegesn,

00:21:48.668 --> 00:21:52.830
m'nekhtikt nisht do o. s'iz akhtsn kilometer tsu der grenets.

00:21:54.051 --> 00:21:55.817
geyt a fur her ikh.

00:21:55.890 --> 00:22:03.292
m'fort fort a familye dortn tsu di mit di v- mit di v- vogn mit di ferd tsu der grenets.

00:22:03.400 --> 00:22:06.869
hobn undz zikh mitgeshlept. akhtsn kilometer.

00:22:07.045 --> 00:22:09.944
m'hot gezogt az dortn iz do der brik vos m'ken adurkhgeyn.

00:22:09.944 --> 00:22:17.299
m'iz tsugekumen tsu der brik, in mitn der nakht, s'hotn geregnt, a kind oyfn vegn hot geveynt az s'geven biter.

00:22:17.457 --> 00:22:20.033
s'geven azoy troyerik oyfn harts altsding.

00:22:22.317 --> 00:22:26.428
m'kumt tsu tsu der brik, di brik iz farmakht. m'ken nisht.

00:22:26.603 --> 00:22:33.903
nor a bisele vayter, efsher a halbn mayl, voynt a yid, der yid voynt dortn yorn, m'iz farforn dortn.

00:22:34.804 --> 00:22:38.881
mir kumen arayn, m'ken nisht araynshteln keyn fus, azoy fil mentshn lign oyf di FLOORn.

00:22:40.542 --> 00:22:42.696
koym mit tsores m'hot zikh arayngeshtupt.

00:22:43.680 --> 00:22:46.627
zogt er undz az in der fri vet araynkumen tsvey daytshn,

00:22:47.410 --> 00:22:50.256
zey nemen tsu tsvey mark fun a perzon,

00:22:50.346 --> 00:22:54.356
un m'revidirt. oyb ets hot epes nemt men tsu.

00:22:55.020 --> 00:22:56.904
ikh hob nisht vos m- moyre tsu hobn.

00:22:58.176 --> 00:23:04.667
in der fri iz arayngekumen tsvey doytshn, m'revidirt altsding, m'hot undz opgelozt.

00:23:06.090 --> 00:23:09.594
tsu undz dray, dray khaveyrim, un ikh fir,

00:23:10.191 --> 00:23:16.648
un ikh hob shoyn dortn mer veyniker gevust vu imer tsu geyn tsu der mumen. ze'mir gegangen.

00:23:17.751 --> 00:23:23.262
di mume hot gevoynt azoy vi ikh hob aykh geshildert. fun di zayt Bug.

00:23:23.455 --> 00:23:26.773
un fun der anderer zayt Bug zenen di rusn geshtanen.

00:23:27.910 --> 00:23:32.814
un di rusn zenen nisht geshtanen punkt oyfn Bug, a bisele vayter,

00:23:33.276 --> 00:23:36.560
un der shtab iz geshtanen fun hekher dortn.

00:23:38.187 --> 00:23:46.837
ANYWAY, iz geven a veldl, zog ikh tsu mayne khaveyrim, "ir ligt do in vald

00:23:47.940 --> 00:23:52.662
s'nisht vayt tsutsugeyn tsu der mumen, ikh vel tsugeyn tsu der mume, ikh vel zen vos tut zikh dortn,

00:23:52.662 --> 00:23:53.942
vel ikh kumen nokh aykh."

00:23:53.863 --> 00:23:57.755
dortn iz ayere froy mitn kind gevezn?

00:23:55.703 --> 00:23:59.004
mayn froy mit di kinder zenen shoyn geven bay di rusn.

00:24:00.192 --> 00:24:08.454
ven zi iz gegangen, s'geven bay a tsvey vokhn befor, iz nokh geven ofn di grenets. un m'hot adurkhgelozt ir.

00:24:11.059 --> 00:24:19.974
s'hot ir epes a doytsh farhaltn, dort iz geven a sakh daytshisher, shoyn geven a sakh doytshn,

00:24:19.974 --> 00:24:22.392
epes hot zi mir gezogt az di da- a daytsh

00:24:22.872 --> 00:24:25.965
hot ir gefregt tsi zi hot gelt, mayses, gesheftn, hot

00:24:25.965 --> 00:24:29.733
hot zi gezogt az zi hot nisht keyn gornisht, hot er nor ir epes tsvontsik mark.

00:24:32.693 --> 00:24:34.155
m'hot ir adurkhgelozt.

00:24:35.747 --> 00:24:38.998
ANYWAY, ikh gey tsu der mumen.

00:24:40.118 --> 00:24:45.646
ikh kum shoyn tsu nenter, shoyn nisht vayt, kuk ikh nisht oyfn dakh,

00:24:45.990 --> 00:24:48.431
ikh vil shoyn arayngeyn INSIDE arayn.

00:24:49.146 --> 00:24:54.104
ober oyfn dakh iz shoyn geshtanen a f- der der der daytshisher fon mitn haknkreyts.

00:24:54.104 --> 00:25:00.159
dortn hot zi shoyn di mume nisht gevoynt. dortn hobn shoyn gevoynt daytshn. S.S.-layte.

00:25:02.089 --> 00:25:06.878
her ikh vi a froy shrayt tsu mir, zi hot mikh gekent. dortn,

00:25:06.878 --> 00:25:09.156
vi ikh hob gezogt, ikh fleg a mol kumen

00:25:09.156 --> 00:25:12.916
tsu der mumen oyf zumer voynung, iz derlebn hot gevoynt a a farmer.

00:25:13.007 --> 00:25:18.485
fleg ikh mit im forn in feld arayn, ikh hob es lib gehat. un er hot mikh zeyer geglikhn.

00:25:19.588 --> 00:25:24.577
iz di dos iz geven di froy vos hot gerufn iz geven a shvester tsu dem farmer.

00:25:24.634 --> 00:25:29.926
un di froy shrayt, "kum aher! kum aher! gey nisht dortn ahin! kum tsurik!"

00:25:30.675 --> 00:25:34.567
ikh hob nisht mikh oryentirt vos zi vil. un ikh gey.

00:25:35.147 --> 00:25:41.841
un gegebn a kum aroys finef S.S.-layte, un "KOMMEN SIE MAL aher!" yo,

00:25:42.657 --> 00:25:48.827
ven ikh bin gegangen tsu der mumen, zenen ongeritn tsvey ofitsirn, doytshn.

00:25:49.879 --> 00:25:52.896
"halt!" ikh bin geblibn shteyn. vu ikh gey.

00:25:52.896 --> 00:25:55.678
dos plats hot geheysn Ruska-Strone.

00:25:56.376 --> 00:26:01.317
zog ikh, ikh gey tsu Ruske-Strone. hobn zey dokh gevust az ikh gey, di S.S. zenen dortn do.

00:26:01.317 --> 00:26:02.866
hobn zey mikh gelozt geyn.

00:26:03.463 --> 00:26:09.746
nor do, azoy vi ikh bin gegangen un un di S.S. zenen gegebn a kum aroys, zey hobn mikh gegebn a UNK,

00:26:09.746 --> 00:26:14.156
iz zi gelofn zogn dem bruder az ikh leb, ikh bin do do.

00:26:14.230 --> 00:26:17.534
iz er gegebn a kum aroys, er hot mikh arumgekhapt,

00:26:17.534 --> 00:26:21.986
du lebst, du lebst! bist, er hot mir gekusht, gefreyt zikh mit mir oysergeveyntlekh.

00:26:22.887 --> 00:26:27.100
un dortn tsvishn zey iz geven eyner, der eltster iz geven an elterer man.

00:26:27.898 --> 00:26:30.035
un er hot gezogt du, daytshn.

00:26:27.965 --> 00:26:29.375
tsvishn di daytshn?

00:26:30.075 --> 00:26:31.928
un er zogt, "du kenst im?"

00:26:31.928 --> 00:26:34.603
"o er iz a fayner loyte UNK."

00:26:34.603 --> 00:26:39.789
zogt er, "nem im tsu zikh arayn in shtub arayn, un du vest im vayzn dem veg,"

00:26:40.150 --> 00:26:45.302
s'geven tsvey un tsvontsik mayl tsu geyn, dort iz geven a brik v- ibern Bug.

00:26:45.302 --> 00:26:47.754
azoy az du kenst dortn vet men kenen geyn.

00:26:49.768 --> 00:26:52.833
er hot mikh arayngenumen in shtub arayn, dertseylt mir der goy,

00:26:53.616 --> 00:26:58.301
az dortn vu di brik iz shteyen daytshn

00:26:59.202 --> 00:27:07.245
un m'ken m'darf nisht geyn nokh der brik, m'ken shoyn geyn nokhn Bug, azoy fil yi- yidn hot men shoyn dortn dertrunken in dem Bug.

00:27:09.327 --> 00:27:11.734
zogt er, "ikh vel dikh nisht firn nokh keyn Bug."

00:27:12.567 --> 00:27:14.327
ANYWAY, er hot mir gegebn optsuesn,

00:27:14.327 --> 00:27:17.319
un ikh hob im gezogt az do lign mayne dray khaveyrim.

00:27:18.810 --> 00:27:24.980
zog ikh, "gey zog zey az du vest zey ba- vest shpeter brengen do aher s'vet vern tunkl."

00:27:25.155 --> 00:27:27.557
er iz gegangen er hot ge- er hot zey gezogt.

00:27:27.557 --> 00:27:30.616
zey zenen gelign biz far nakht dortn.

00:27:32.226 --> 00:27:36.455
far nakht iz gegangen der daytsh, yo ven ikh bin geven bay dem poyer,

00:27:36.563 --> 00:27:41.147
hot er mir arayngebrengt tsvontsik CIGARETTES, der alter daytsh.

00:27:41.457 --> 00:27:43.510
er hot nisht gevolt bay mir nemen keyn gelt.

00:27:44.832 --> 00:27:49.264
un er iz gegangen far nakht er hot genumen er hot tseshikt

00:27:49.455 --> 00:27:53.178
di di di di S.S. oyf farshidene punktn,

00:27:53.438 --> 00:27:59.742
un er mit dem poyer hobn gebrengt tsu trogn oyf di pleytses a shifl,

00:28:00.795 --> 00:28:02.729
m'hot es aropgelozt in vaser arayn,

00:28:03.647 --> 00:28:07.775
un er hot mir ongezogt az ikh zol nisht zitsn nor ikh zol lign.

00:28:08.271 --> 00:28:11.069
vayl, zogt er, "ikh hob nokh keyn mentsh nisht geharget," zogt er,

00:28:11.069 --> 00:28:13.277
"in fertstn yor bin ikh do gevezn.

00:28:14.768 --> 00:28:18.677
un ikh vil dikh do oykh nisht m'zol dir hargenen, vayl az di rusn zen

00:28:18.733 --> 00:28:23.385
a bay aza shifl mit a man zitst, shist men. zolst lign."

00:28:23.965 --> 00:28:31.485
nor vos den, der poyer, er vil ikh zol im shikn mitn poyer shtraykh-holts. zaplkes.

00:28:31.778 --> 00:28:34.050
du veyst vos zaplkes, MATCHES.

00:28:35.710 --> 00:28:39.315
ANYWAY, ikh hob mikh arayngezetst in di shifl un zikh avekgeleygt

00:28:39.439 --> 00:28:41.677
un der poyer hot mikh adurkh geshift,

00:28:41.852 --> 00:28:45.120
un er hot mikh arayngefirt tsu mayn froy.

00:28:46.864 --> 00:28:48.427
ikh bin arayngekumen tsu mayn froy,

00:28:49.024 --> 00:28:53.304
un shtel dikh for, m'hot zikh derfreyt azoy vayter, vayl zi hot nisht gevust,

00:28:53.563 --> 00:28:58.180
s'dortn di mishpokhe hot zi gezogt, er iz geblibn in Varshe, ikh veys nisht vos iz mit im geshen.

00:29:00.702 --> 00:29:01.860
ANYWAY,

00:29:03.199 --> 00:29:06.112
ikh bin gekumen m'iz gevezn dortn, BUT,

00:29:06.098 --> 00:29:08.441
vifl tsayt zent ir dort geblibn?

00:29:08.667 --> 00:29:12.103
mit di vifl tsayt zent ir dort geblibn?

00:29:08.807 --> 00:29:09.567
PARDON ME?

00:29:10.388 --> 00:29:12.069
dortn gevezn?

00:29:12.227 --> 00:29:18.397
ikh bin ongekumen dortn ahin, iz gevezn di END OF september.

00:29:19.652 --> 00:29:25.316
oder nayn un tsvontsikstn akht un tsvontsik zenen bin ikh ongekumen dortn ahin,

00:29:25.727 --> 00:29:31.175
un mir hobn gevoynt dortn biz MAY.
